This is SEOAgent, an open-source agent-first SEO toolkit.

Architecture: TypeScript pnpm monorepo with 4 packages.
- packages/core/ — ALL business logic lives here. Start here for any feature.
- packages/cli/ — commander.js CLI, thin wrapper over core
- packages/mcp/ — MCP server (24 tools), thin wrapper over core
- packages/dashboard/ — Vite + React + Tailwind local web UI

Key files:
- packages/core/src/index.ts — barrel export (public API)
- packages/core/src/types.ts — shared types
- packages/core/src/schema.ts — SQLite schema (9 tables)
- packages/core/src/__tests__/ — all core tests (231 tests)

Workflow: TDD. Write test first, implement, verify, export from index.ts.
Tests use vitest with globals. Mock HTTP calls, use SEOAGENT_HOME env var for temp dirs.
Build: pnpm build. Test: pnpm test.

See AGENTS.md for full function reference and patterns.
